// Warrior Map Formatting
ItemDisplay[MAG (ARMOR OR WEAPON) !ID (MAPID=181 OR MAPID=182)]: %RED%* %BLUE%%NAME% %RED%[C] *%CONTINUE%
ItemDisplay[RARE (ARMOR OR WEAPON) !ID (MAPID=181 OR MAPID=182)]: %RED%* %YELLOW%%NAME% %RED%[C] *%CONTINUE%
